            It seems to me&#x2014;and this is the relevance to the debate that we are having&#x2014;that the particular issue that my noble friend Lord Brooke raised and to which the noble Baroness, Lady Noakes, referred is not the slightest bit solved by the amendment. An Information
            
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_101gc' title='Col. 101GC &mdash; HL Deb 02 March 2005 vol 670 c101GC' name='column_101gc' href='#column_101gc' rel='bookmark'>101GC</a>
