          <p class='first-para'>
            I shall not rise to that. I was merely remarking that the assault which now has police-level penalties extends police-type treatments to a wider number of public servants, who are operating perfectly ordinary administrative functions. I regret that development; I shall phrase it in those terms. I shall want to consider carefully and possibly return to the clause on Report.</p><p>
